casebody.data:
Donald HEMPHILL, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Jiab SULEIMAN, D.O., Jiab Suleiman, D.O., P.C., and Premier Orthopedics, L.L.C., Defendants-Appellants. SC: 155464
COA: 335351 Supreme Court of Michigan. October 30, 2018

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for reconsideration of this Court's July 13, 2018 order is considered, and it is DENIED, because it does not appear that the order was entered erroneously.
